Info:
Create and edit with precision 
Animation Wizard walks you through creating an animation sequence. 
Add video or other animation as separate frame objects or image, 
text, animated text. Use the frame Panel with filmstrip view to 
easily create object animation.

Powerful Optimization
Apply various text effects, video effects, transitions and even 
Photoshop compatible filters . Ensure fast-loading animation by 
using the optimization wizard to automate compression based on 
presets.

Flexible Output
Enjoy a variety of output options by creating True Color AVI, 
QuickTime, MPEG. Generating HTML files to display GIF animation 
in web browsers or save objects as multi-layered PhotoImpact and 
Photoshop files.
